---
title: Malaysian-Style Pork & Veggie Stir-Fry with Garlic & Ginger Rice
description: The perfect sauce is here, so make room in your pan for an oyster sauce that can take a pork and veggie stir-fry to stardom.
Sealing this stir-fry’s rightful place is garlic and ginger rice - we give it a gold star for sure!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/651dfc105dddf9d92d88d64c-a73b2946.jpeg
